HEADWORD: Scrabbed eggs
<hw>Scrab"bed eggs`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[CF.
<er>Scramble</er>.]</ety> <def>A Lenten dish, composed of eggs boiled
hard, chopped, and seasoned with butter, salt, and pepper.</def>
<rj><au>Halliwell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
